\chapter{The Library}

	For the specification of transformation rules one usually
	needs all kinds of auxiliary functions to achieve local
	transformations. Examples are all kinds of operations on
	lists, renaming of bound variables and substitution. The
	strategy language comes with a library of predefined
	strategies for this purpose. 

